================================================================================
MODIFICATIONS FROM ORIGINAL LIBFREENECT2
================================================================================

This fork diverges significantly from the original libfreenect2 project:

1. PLATFORM FOCUS
   - macOS 11+ only (Big Sur and newer)
   - Apple Silicon (arm64) native support
   - Removed Windows and Linux support

2. GPU COMPUTE
   - Added Metal compute shader pipeline for depth processing
   - Removed CUDA support (not available on macOS)
   - Removed VAAPI support (Linux-only)
   - Removed TegraJPEG support (NVIDIA Jetson-only)

3. BUILD SYSTEM
   - macOS Framework build target
   - CMakePresets for Xcode integration
   - Homebrew dependency paths (Apple Silicon + Intel)

4. CODE CLEANUP
   - Removed Linux udev rules
   - Removed Windows UsbDk driver code
   - Simplified to macOS-only code paths

